# ============================================================
# CIVILIZATION DEAD LETTER FLOW
# ============================================================

status: canonical
layer: 050.flow
system: civilization-os
owner: Boss
prepared_by: Zero

purpose:
Define the canonical dead-letter flow.

flow_steps:
1 terminal failure is classified
2 unit is marked dead-lettered
3 final failure trace is recorded
4 operator-visible escalation remains available
5 dead-lettered unit is excluded from infinite retry loops

terminal_failure_examples:
- incompatible contract
- unauthorized target
- invalid payload after retry exhaustion
